metadata.dc:description: A 30 year old patient with idiopathic thrombocytosis received chemotherapy and developed amenorrhea and secondary ovarian failure. After discontinuation of chemotherapy, she became pregnant and recovered normal ovarian function 6 months after delivery.
metadata.dc:title: Embarazo en una paciente con falla ovárica prematura secundaria a quimioterapia.
[Pregnancy in a patient with premature ovarian failure secondary to chemotherapy].
